---
layout: _default
---
<article class="o-post">
  <header class="m-post-header">
    <h1>
      <a href="{{ url }}">{{ title }}</a>
    </h1>

    <p class="a-timestamp">
      Published <time>{{ page.date | date: "%B %e, %Y" }}</time>
    </p>
  </header>

  <div class="m-post-body">
    {{ content }}
  </div>
</article>

<div class="a-callout-box m-blog-cta">
  <img
    class="a-headshot"
    src="/images/headshot.jpg"
    alt="Evan Minto looking up and slightly smiling. He’s a young white man with medium-length hair and black plastic glasses."
  >

  <h2>Let’s Do Some Work Together</h2>

  <p>
    Hey there! My name is Evan Minto and I offer freelance services for
    web UX design and UI development, accessibility, inclusive design,
    pop culture reviews and analysis, live event and video hosting,
    and more. Do you have an interesting project you need some help with?
    <a href="/contact">Let’s talk.</a>
  </p>
</div>
